  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fiora is a roguelike game in which you will see randomly generated maps, you need to fight shadows, and along the way collect firewood to maintain the flame of Fiora, without which you will not be able to use magic. <br>Feel the dynamic gameplay unusual for this genre, use dodge, think through the route, push obstacles if they interfere with your path :)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/2313a72e76b93631d39e22de1765ab8e.poster.avif?t=1769597528\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/2313a72e76b93631d39e22de1765ab8e.webm?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/2313a72e76b93631d39e22de1765ab8e.mp4?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect crystal oil to improve the characteristics of your weapons. At the moment, the game has three types of weapons, four classes, and the ability to improve it to +20, the main thing is not to forget that when improving, the weapon can break and disappear from your inventory<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/60229028f59f3a37f4e9ae86313e52cb.poster.avif?t=1769597528\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/60229028f59f3a37f4e9ae86313e52cb.webm?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/60229028f59f3a37f4e9ae86313e52cb.mp4?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight bosses and special opponents that appear from time to time, or during certain events<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/9f52885193ef2f7c2239dbb11b891339.poster.avif?t=1769597528\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/9f52885193ef2f7c2239dbb11b891339.webm?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/9f52885193ef2f7c2239dbb11b891339.mp4?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fiora is a roguelike game in which you will see randomly generated maps, you need to fight shadows, and along the way collect firewood to maintain the flame of Fiora, without which you will not be able to use magic. <br>Feel the dynamic gameplay unusual for this genre, use dodge, think through the route, push obstacles if they interfere with your path :)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/2313a72e76b93631d39e22de1765ab8e.poster.avif?t=1769597528\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/2313a72e76b93631d39e22de1765ab8e.webm?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/2313a72e76b93631d39e22de1765ab8e.mp4?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect crystal oil to improve the characteristics of your weapons. At the moment, the game has three types of weapons, four classes, and the ability to improve it to +20, the main thing is not to forget that when improving, the weapon can break and disappear from your inventory<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/60229028f59f3a37f4e9ae86313e52cb.poster.avif?t=1769597528\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/60229028f59f3a37f4e9ae86313e52cb.webm?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/60229028f59f3a37f4e9ae86313e52cb.mp4?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight bosses and special opponents that appear from time to time, or during certain events<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/9f52885193ef2f7c2239dbb11b891339.poster.avif?t=1769597528\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/9f52885193ef2f7c2239dbb11b891339.webm?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/9f52885193ef2f7c2239dbb11b891339.mp4?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
